lead_paragraph: Andrea Petkovic of Germany eliminated fourth-seeded Garbine Muguruza 6-1, 5-7, 6-2 to reach the Qatar Open semifinals on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Petkovic Ousts Muguruza to Reach Qatar Semis
